,“ Lasers in surgery and medicine, sv. 42, č. 6, pp. 510-518, 2010.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[15]&amp;nbsp;P. Fiore, F. Panza, G. Cassatella, A. Russo, V.&amp;nbsp;Frisardi,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;V. Solfrizzi, M. Ranieri, L. Di Teo a A. Santamato, „Short-term effects of high-intensity laser therapy versus ultrasound therapy in the treatment of low back pain: a randomized controlled trial,“ Eur J Phys Rehabil Med, sv. 47, č. 3, pp. 367-373, 2011.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[16]&amp;nbsp;J. Zeredo, K. Sasaki a K. Toda, „High-intensity laser for acupuncture-like stimulation,“ Lasers in medical science, sv. 22, č. 1, pp. 37-41, 2007.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[17]&amp;nbsp;S. Wu a R. Maloney, „Low-level laser therapy: a possi- ble new light on wound healing,“ Podiatry Management, sv.&amp;nbsp;27,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;pp. 105-110, 2008.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[1]&amp;nbsp;A. Santamato, V. Solfrizzi, F. Panza, G. Tondi, V. Frisardi, B. G. Leggin, M. Ranieri a P. Fiore, „Short-term effects of high-intensity laser therapy versus ultrasound therapy in the treatment of people with subacromial impingement syndrome: a randomized clinical trial,“ Physical therapy, sv. 89, č. 7, pp. 643- 652, 2009.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[2]&amp;nbsp;T. Ninomiya, Y. Miyamoto, T. Ito, A. Yamashita, M. Wakita a T. Nishisaka, „High-intensity pulsed laser irradiation accelerates bone formation in metaphyseal trabecular bone in rat femur,“ Journal of bone and mineral metabolism, sv. 21, č. 2, pp. 67-73, 2003.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[3]&amp;nbsp;J. Marotti, F. F. Sperandio, E. R. Fregnani, A. C. C. Aranha, P. M. de Freitas a C. de Paula Eduardo, „High-intensity laser and photodynamic therapy as a treatment for recurrent herpes labialis,“ Photomedicine and Laser Surgery, sv. 28, č. 3, pp. 439- 444, 2010.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[4]&amp;nbsp;K.&amp;nbsp;A.&amp;nbsp;Larkin,&amp;nbsp;J.&amp;nbsp;S.&amp;nbsp;Martin,&amp;nbsp;E.&amp;nbsp;H.&amp;nbsp;Zeanah,&amp;nbsp;J.&amp;nbsp;M.&amp;nbsp;True,&amp;nbsp;R.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;W. Braith a P. A. Borsa, „Limb Blood Flow After Class 4 Laser Therapy,“ Journal of Athletic Training, sv. 47, č. 2, pp. 178-183, 2012.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[5]&amp;nbsp;J. Kozarev a Z. Vizintin, „Novel laser therapy in treatment of onychomycosis,“ Journal of the Laser and Health Academy, sv. 1, pp. 1-8,&amp;nbsp;2010.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[6]&amp;nbsp;L. G. Hochman, „Laser treatment of onychomycosis using a novel 0.65-millisecond pulsed Nd: YAG 1064-nm laser,“ Journal of Cosmetic and Laser Therapy, sv. 13, č. 1, pp. 2-5,&amp;nbsp;2011.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[7]&amp;nbsp;A. Giuliani, M. Fernandez, M. Farinelli, L. Baratto, R. Capra, G. Rovetta, P. Monteforte, L. Giardino a L. Calza, „Very low level laser therapy attenuates edema and pain in experimental models,“ International journal of tissue reactions, sv. 26, pp. 29- 38, 2004.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[8]&amp;nbsp;D. Fortuna, G. Rossi, T. W. Bilotta, A. Zati, V.&amp;nbsp;Gazzotti,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A. Venturini, S. Pinna, C. Serra a L. Masotti, „High-intensity laser therapy during chronic degenerative tenosynovitis experimentally induced in broiler chickens,“ v Society of Photo-Optical Instru- mentation Engineers (SPIE) Conference Series, 2002.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[9]&amp;nbsp;L. Brosseau, V. Robinson, G. Wells, R. Debie, A.&amp;nbsp;Gam,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;K. Harman, M. Morin, B. Shea a P. Tugwell, „Low level laser therapy (Classes I, II and III) for treating rheumatoid arthritis,“ Cochrane Database Syst Rev, sv. 4, 2005.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('134','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;Laser Hemorrhidoplasty procedure (III, IV Grade) consists of interstitial introduction of laser light with the wavelength of 1470 nm by means of optical fiber with the sharp end. The procedure is performed under local anesthesia. It lasts for about 15 minutes. Normal daily activity is possible after the treatment. The risk of complications is negligible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;The light of&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;the 1470 nm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;laser is characterized by&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;a several dozen higher absorption in water&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in comparison with older generation lasers (810, 980 and 1064nm). Due to the fact that tissues contain significant amount of water, the change of absorption of light from hemoglobin to water protects the patients against deep penetration in the surrounding tissues. Controlled emission of laser energy obliterates the nodes from the insight, not destroying both the mucosa and the sphincter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202007/1596014809940e61.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot; width=&quot;394&quot; height=&quot;280&quot; style=&quot;float: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:15px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;The advantages of the procedure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Owing to the homogenous radial emission of light with Dila 1470nm diode laser the following are obtained:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Tissue reduction in hemorrhoid cushions (of the single segment or around the entire circumference).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Maximal retention of muscle tissue or mucosa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Restoration of natural anatomical structure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;No risk of sphincter damage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:25px;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;background:rgb(255,255,255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;Owing to the fact that no incision or stitching are use, the healing process in extremely fast. Patients experience less pot-operative pain and can come back to normal activity more quickly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:25px;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;background:rgb(255,255,255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;No incision,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:25px;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;background:rgb(255,255,255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;No stitching,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;No open wounds.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;This technique is safe and causes minimal pain or discomfort to the patient. Post operative recovery is faster than alternative approaches, with only few complications. Anesthesia or analgesia are generally no longer required what greatly reduces complications, whilst simplifying the procedure and making the treatment safer, faster and completely outpatient with minimal or no pain postoperatively for the patient, showing excellent immediate and long term results.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('136','1','4','&lt;h1 style=&quot;;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;1. It is capable of eliminating fat that we cannot make disappear with exercise or diet&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;Certain areas of the body in both men and women (thighs, abdomen, knees or ankles), can accumulate fat due to hormonal and / or genetic causes.&amp;nbsp;In case of trying to perform diets or exercises to eliminate these accumulations of fat, we can see how these areas are not reduced, they can even become more evident by reducing the volume of the surrounding areas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 48px 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;The lipolytic effect of Laserlipolisis is capable of reducing fat cells without damaging or affecting the surrounding tissues, thereby dissolving excess fat selectively.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;2. Laserlipolysis allows treating the most difficult areas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;The complicated areas are those that have a thin dermis, a complicated retraction of the skin, aged skin, skin with irregular areas,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://faceclinic.es/eliminar-cartucheras/&quot; title=&quot;Delete holsters&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;removing catheters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px;margin-right: 48px;margin-bottom: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;For example, the area or inner face of the arms and thighs, love handles at the waist, anterior aspect of the knees, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;They are areas with which good results are not obtained by performing&amp;nbsp;traditional&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://faceclinic.es/cirugia-estetica-corporal/liposuccion-madrid/&quot; title=&quot;Liposuction Madrid&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;liposuction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;.&amp;nbsp;Laserlipolysis is a precise technique that will&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;reduce the accumulated fat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in the most complicated areas, in addition to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;retracting the skin in the area, thus avoiding flaccidity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin: 21px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;3. No hospitalization necessary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;It is performed on an outpatient basis.&amp;nbsp;The intervention lasts about an hour depending on the area to be treated, and after the procedure you can return to the home immediately on your own feet.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin: 21px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;4. It is carried out with local anesthesia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;It is normally performed under local anesthesia, and due to the technical characteristics, the appearance of bruising is minimal and recovery is very fast.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin: 21px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;5. It is capable of contracting the skin eliminating sagging&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px;margin-right: 48px;margin-bottom: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Unlike Liposuction, this technique, in addition to destroying the adipocytes, contracts the skin, readjusting it naturally to our new body contour.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;This contraction is essential to achieve an excellent aesthetic result, since the Lipolaser favors the production of new collagen fibers, improving the skin&amp;#39;s texture.&amp;nbsp;In other cases, a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://faceclinic.es/cirugia-estetica-corporal/abdominoplastia/&quot; title=&quot;Abdominoplasty Madrid&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;tummy tuck&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;is necessary&amp;nbsp;to remove all the excess skin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin: 21px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;6. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-left: 21px;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Symbol;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;With this equipment we can&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;selectively destroy fat and retract skin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-left: 21px;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Symbol;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;It allows us to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;personalize&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;the treatment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-left: 21px;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Symbol;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Due to the coagulant effect, we reduce bleeding and bruising, making&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;recovery much faster.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-left: 21px;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Symbol;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;It allows us to work with high precision in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;most delicate areas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;7. Recovery is quick and comfortable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;Since it is a much less aggressive technique than traditional liposuction, it will facilitate the incorporation into normal life quickly and comfortably.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;The only care that the patient will have to take is to keep the girdle recommended by the specialist in place, and not to do impact sports in the first weeks.&amp;nbsp;The return to work is immediate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin: 21px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;8. The possibility of scarring is reduced&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;The cannula used is so small that the incisions that are made are minimal and almost imperceptible after the intervention.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin: 21px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;9. Highly satisfactory results&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px;margin-right: 48px;margin-bottom: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;The results of this technique are very satisfactory, since we eliminate difficult fat, we correct the body contour and the skin adapts to the areas we treat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;In this way we achieve &amp;quot;double&amp;quot; aesthetic results, which are not achieved with traditional Liposuction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin: 21px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 24px&quot;&gt;10. Laserlipolysis as the treatment to end accumulated fat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 12px 0 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px&quot;&gt;And it is that it has become the least painful surgical intervention that requires less time both in the operating room and recovery.&amp;nbsp;It only requires a slight incision to introduce the small needle-like cannula, an incision that is &amp;quot;imperceptible&amp;quot; after surgery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px;margin-right: 48px;margin-bottom: 0;padding: 0;vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;As benefits compared to other techniques, the greater retraction of the skin stands out, that is, it prevents sagging skin, tightening it, and decreases inflammation.&amp;nbsp;The laser melts the fat and then removes it from the body.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:12px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;color: rgb(56, 56, 56);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 17px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('137','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;DOD diode laser &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;provides you with state-of-the-art laser technology for a safe and simple treatment in urology. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;Whether BPH, TULA (bladder tumors), partial kidney resection and various other applications, our laser procedure incorporates both highly advanced laser systems and suitable fibers which bring true definitive care. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;The result is a minimally invasive treatment with enhanced patient benefits such as quick recovery, local anesthesia, and minimal post-treatment side effects or discomforts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202008/1596791147afe945.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:35px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(252, 131, 34);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 18px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Biophysical characteristics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Roboto;color:rgb(122,122,122);font-size:12px&quot;&gt;Following features of the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;color:rgb(122,122,122);font-size:12px&quot;&gt;DOD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Roboto;color:rgb(122,122,122);font-size:12px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;diode laser make it very useful instrument in prostate surgery:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;The 980 nm wavelength of the laser provides the highest combined absorption in water and hemoglobin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;As prostate tissue contains high percentage of water, our laser vaporizes it very effectively. Absorption of the laser energy by hemoglobin leads to excellent haemostasis and precise ablation of the obstructing tissue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;Equal absorption in tissue either well or poor supplied with blood-optimal penetration depth regardless of the level of vascularization ( vs. KPT, Hol, Thu)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;Enables precise, minimally carbonized and virtually bloodless incision in prostatic tissue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;Excellent haemostasis ensures minimal post-operative bleeding and preservation of surrounding tissue for a quick recovery ( vs. KPT, TURP )&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);font-size: 12px&quot;&gt;Short time of the procedure( vs. Ho;YAG, Nd:YAG, KPT, Thu )&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('138','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202008/1597216474ba3e7a.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot; width=&quot;456&quot; height=&quot;253&quot; style=&quot;float: right; width: 459px; height: 281px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;1.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;1) Patient sitting on treatment bed with therapist standing behind patient.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;2) Find the trigger point on the trapezius muscle and the tension in the muscle through palpation and cervical mobility examination.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;3) Calculate treatment area, Eg. length*width (approximately 45 cm²).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202008/1597217664782023.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot; width=&quot;456&quot; height=&quot;253&quot; style=&quot;float: right; width: 456px; height: 253px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;1) After the examination, select the appropriate treatment mode on the host and set the treatment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202008/1597217839341905.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot; width=&quot;456&quot; height=&quot;253&quot; style=&quot;float: right;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;area.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: norma