o as to achieve the purpose of fat-dissolving weight loss.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;7.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The advantages of lipolysis?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;The operation is gentle and the doctor&amp;#39;s labor intensity is low&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;It can achieve precise weight loss, such as double chin, butterfly sleeves,get rid of eye bag.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;;line-height:36px;background:rgb(248,249,250)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;Small mechanical damage to the tissue and quick recovery after operation;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;;line-height:36px;background:rgb(248,249,250)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;The laser can coagulate small blood vessels, reducing the amount of bleeding during the operation;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;;line-height:36px;background:rgb(248,249,250)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;5.The fat-dissolving effect is meticulous and uniform;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;6.Not easy to rebound, increase the elasticity of the skin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;7.Can be used for dense fat pads and irregular treatment after liposuction that are difficult to solve with traditional negative pressure liposuction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('141','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(113, 112, 116); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;High Intensity Laser (HIL) technology is based on the well-known principle of low level laser therapy (LLLT). High power and choice of the right wavelength allow for deep tissue penetration. HIL offers powerful and non-addictive form of pain management. Through a natural process of energy transfer (biostimulation and photomechanical effect) it speeds up healing and regeneration. HIL is particularly effective in treatment of sport injuries, e.g. muscle strain or joint distortion, and back pain caused by e.g. herniated disc or disorders in the cervical region causing neck pain.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202008/15979133595d7263.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The lasers we use are ‘hot lasers’. These lasers are much more powerful than cold lasers normally more than 100x more powerful. Therapy with these lasers feels warm and soothing because of the higher energy. This therapy is known as ‘High Intensity Laser Therapy’ (HILT).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202008/15979133994e2428.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('142','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Laser lipolysis -&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;a procedure for removing excess fat tissue with the use of a laser.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Devices designed to perform laser lipolysis treatments have been designed to remove excess body fat. The basis of their operation is the use of selective interaction between the laser beam and adipose tissue. Treatments of this type in November 2006 were approved for performance in the USA, after obtaining a certificate from the American FDA (Food and Drug Administration).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Laser fat reduction treatments are a new standard in the techniques of removing excess fat in order to model the body shape. Since these are body shaping procedures, they are not intended for very obese people who want to achieve the effect of a significant weight reduction. In this group of people (who are significantly overweight), the broadly understood prophylaxis should be initially introduced in combination with other treatment methods, e.g. classic liposuction. And laser lipolysis should be performed after them for even better clinical results. This sequence of procedures in this group of patients results from the fact that during one laser lipolysis treatment the reduction of adipose tissue is approximately 500 ml.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Laser lipolysis treatments allow you to reduce the excessive amount of adipose tissue in areas that are particularly &amp;quot;resistant&amp;quot; to diets and exercise, such as:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● face, neck - laser lipolysis treatments give the possibility of modeling the shape of the face, including by removing the double chin,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● arms,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● stomach,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● chest (removal of gynecomastia in men),&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● waist, hips,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● back,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● buttocks,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● knee and thigh area,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● pubic area&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today, body modeling is becoming more and more common, allowing lipolysis to be included in the group of the most popular treatments performed all over the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Lipolysis treatment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;(treatment duration 45-60 minutes depending on the area)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Due to the use of very thin optical fibers (300 µm and 600 µm in diameter) during the procedures, introduced with the help of special cannulas with a diameter of about 1 mm, laser lipolysis treatments are classified as minimally invasive procedures that do not require general anesthesia. These procedures are performed under local anesthesia (usually tumescent). The heat generated during the treatment, as a result of the laser beam-tissue interaction, allows, in addition to reducing excess body fat, also to improve the texture, elasticity and elasticity of the skin. Thanks to the use of a high-power laser during the lipolysis procedure, body contouring is associated with a shorter recovery time and a reduction in the possibility of many side effects arising during traditional liposuction. Patients are usually able to return to normal activities 1-2 days after surgery. In order to improve the effectiveness of the therapy, doctors recommend wearing an elastic compression dressing or using special compression garments for a period of about one week after the procedure and a short course of antibiotics to avoid infection. In some cases, gentle massages of the healing areas and endermology treatments are also recommended after about 10 days after the procedure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you are looking for a safe, modern and effective method of body shaping, laser lipolysis is the best choice for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Before laser lipolysis is performed, consultation and qualification for the procedure by a doctor is required, who will also present you with other therapeutic options depending on your needs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FAQ&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Who are laser lipolysis treatments for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The best candidate for laser lipolysis treatments is a person:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● a person in good general health, physically active and with a body weight slightly above the ideal weight.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● An individual with one or more unnecessary clumps of body fat that did not appear to change in volume through exercise and diet.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● a person who is disturbed by thicker parts of the body and is motivated to remove them surgically, but does not have much time for a long postoperative return to normal activity after surgery.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● person in need of skin firmness improvement in order to combat cellulite.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● a person who underwent classic liposuction, who had symptoms of &amp;quot;saggy&amp;quot; and uneven skin after the procedure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. What effects can be expected from laser lipolysis treatments?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● Laser lipolysis provides:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● permanent destruction of fat cells,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● firming and elasticizing the skin,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● no symptom of &amp;quot;sagging, loose skin&amp;quot; after the procedure,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● cellulite reduction,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● quick recovery after the procedure,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● only point marks in the places where the cannulas are inserted,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● minimal risk of complications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Can laser lipolysis treatments be performed after classic liposuction?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Laser lipolysis is a new, innovative method that allows you to achieve spectacular results in body shaping and is often used as a procedure that corrects the shortcomings of traditional liposuction.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. What are the contraindications to laser lipolysis treatments?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Contraindications to laser lipolysis treatments are:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● poor general health,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● epilepsy,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;●&amp;nbsp;multiple sclerosis,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● kidney and liver disease,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● diabetes,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● thyroid disease,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;● blood coagulation disorders.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;(The aforementioned diseases do not exclude the procedure definitively - in such cases a doctor-specialist consultation is necessary).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. When and what effects can be expected after the treatment?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After laser lipolysis, the body shape gradually improves day by day. The circumference of the treated areas of the body is gradually reduced and the skin becomes firmer and tighter. The final results obtained after the laser lipolysis treatment are permanent. The above effects appear gradually after 1 - 2 months. In some cases, this process may take up to six months. In the event of weight gain again, the fat will be deposited in places other than those from which it was treated.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. How fast is the return to normal activity after laser lipolysis?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After traditional liposuction procedures, the time to return to normal activity usually requires from several weeks to even several months. The laser lipolysis treatment drastically shortens the convalescence period and after 1-2 days most patients return to normal activity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. What is the post-treatment period?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After the procedure, the patient stays in the recovery room, where he remains until the anesthetic drugs administered during the procedure stop working. After a maximum of several hours, you can leave the center. The use of local anesthesia allows you to exclude the side effects typical of procedures performed under general anesthesia (such as nausea or malaise).Immediately after the treatment, slight bruising and swelling of the tissues may occur, as well as slight numbness of the treated areas. They usually disappear within a few days after the procedure. The swelling disappears after about a week.For each patient, the doctor gives individual special instructions on how to proceed in the period after the procedure. The aim of appropriate therapies during the recovery period is to maximize the effect of the treatment while reducing the risk of complications. The doctor also determines the schedule of follow-up visits after the procedure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8. How long does laser lipolysis take?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A typical treatment for one area of the body takes about 20 to 60 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9. How many lipolysis treatments should be performed in order to obtain optimal clinical results?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In most cases, it is enough to perform one laser lipolysis treatment to obtain the expected clinical effects. If the patient expects further improvement in specific areas, another follow-up treatment can be performed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10. Can laser lipolysis treatments be performed in places inaccessible to traditional liposuction?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Yes. Especially in areas such as the face, neck, back or knees, where standard liposuction can only be performed to a limited extent or is not possible at all.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11. Do laser lipolysis treatments fight cellulite?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Laser lipolysis treatments are used as part of a combination therapy in the treatment of cellulite.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12. Is the laser lipolysis treatment painful?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Est laser lipolysis procedure is performed under local anesthesia, therefore it is not a painful procedure. The discomfort experienced by the patient during the procedure is minimal. Most often, patients feel a slight stinging or the feeling of stretching the skin.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;13.Advantages of&amp;nbsp; lipolysis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;An indispensable advantage of laser lipolysis is that, compared to traditional (surgical) face lifting, it does not require a long period of convalescence and does not exclude the patient from everyday activities for a long time - apart from swelling and minor bruises, there are usually no other side effects. However, you must remember to use cosmetics with a delicate and non-irritating composition after the treatment, avoid sunbathing and for a certain period not use other treatments in the field of aesthetic dermatology and surgery.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('143','1','4','&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(122, 122, 122); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Endovenous occlusion of great saphenous vain and small saphenus vain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(122, 122, 122); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The procedure is performed under local anesthesia either in an outpatient setting or in the operating room.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(122, 122, 122); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The endovenous method leaves no scars, minimizes the risk of infection and post procedural pain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(122, 122, 122); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;It also gives excellent clinical and esthetical outcome with significant cost reduction.&amp;nbsp;A distinctive post procedural pain decrease can be observed after 1470 nm laser treatment due to better light absorption inside the vein &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(122, 122, 122); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;(40 times better than the wave of the 980 nm laser and&amp;nbsp;160 times better than the wave of the Nd: YAG 1064 nm laser).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202008/15985797380eadf7.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202008/159857976352ed15.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The DOD Laser 980nm 1470 nm Diode Laser is an advanced system that protocols to maximize the comfort, safety, speed, and effectiveness of varicose vein treatments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;It is portable, user friendly, and versatile laser product, with minimum to none maintenance for the best and most cost-effective treatment of all types of venous insufficiencies. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The compact, table-top sized, and accurate DOD Laser system is developed with 980nm and 1470 nm wavelength for endovenous vascular closure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('144','1','4','&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;Vascular Removal Treatment Principle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;How it works?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;A beam of light is transmitted through a small, smooth, flat glass hand piece which is gently placed on the skin. During the treatment, the&amp;nbsp;Laser System&amp;nbsp;wave length is absorbed into target are being the broken capillaries .It has a heating effect on the target causing it to disperse.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;How does it feel?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;You may feel a sting, like the snapping of a small rubber band each time the&amp;nbsp;Laser System is applied to the skin, although the&amp;nbsp;Laser System&amp;nbsp;head does have built in cooling so this will take away from any discomfort you may experience in the skin and make the treatment more pleasant.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;What to expect?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Immediately following the treatment, your skin may feel quite warm and may have a stinging sensation like sunburnt skin, which will calm down over a couple of hours, this is a desired reaction as we want to successfully heat the skin to the point of having a successful effect on the target area.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;What areas can I treat?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Most common areas to treat are face, nose and cheek areas. Please Note: the desired area for treatment needs to be out of the sun for 4-6 weeks prior treatment and then continually throughout the rest of treatment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;How many treatments are recommended?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:8px;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(249,249,249)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;We recommend 3-6 treatments, there is a 1-2 week waiting period between each treatment, but you do often see improvements after each session.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('145','1','4','&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Specially developed glass tips assure working without fiber degradation and consistently high performance. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;More fiber control through tactile feedback shows the best outcome and permits outstanding treatment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 25px 0;text-indent: 0;padding: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The DOD Laser application is the first true laser to combine the efficacy of trans-urethral resection with the unmatched safety and hemostasis of the laser systems. The patent pending glass tip of the fiber ensures a safe treatment of benign prostatic hyperplasia.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202009/159904085261fe19.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202009/15990408848e3c59.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202009/1599040919a79306.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202009/1599040951ffdae0.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('147','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Intra-discal ablations on disc prolapses with unimpaired anulus fibrosus are indicated for the region of the lumbar spine as well as the cervical spine. The minimally invasive pain management via atrophy of the pain receptors is another ideal field of application for DOD&amp;nbsp;diode laser.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The surgical operations are carried out on an outpatient basis with local anesthesia and under strict MRI/CT-control when conservative treatment methods fail to achieve the desired healing process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202009/1600077232c7e629.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202009/16000772616dcea9.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202009/16000772775af182.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('148','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;DOD Diode Laser provides various treatment options with a 600 micron optical fiber, a guide wire introducer sheath, and a needle for percutaneous perforation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Operating Steps:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;1. Prior to treatment, the SFJ and GSV are mapped through the use of color duplex ultrasound. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;2. The guide wire introducer sheath is introduced into the GSV at knee level or the lower part of the thigh. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;3. The fiber is advanced via the introducer sheath until the fiber tip is positioned 1-2 cm distal to the SFJ. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;4. A red guiding light emitted from the fiber tip provides a helpful indication of the tip position. Prior to release of the laser beam, the exact tip position is controlled carefully by use of ultrasound.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The method has been well tolerated by the majority of the patients treated, with only occasional feelings of heat during treatment. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Most patients show mild ecchymosis and occasional mild induration and paresthesia in the area of anaesthetic infiltration. It is expected that the undesired side-effect incidence will decrease as the operators gain more experience in the use of this new technique. The results were evaluated by the physicians as well as patients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('149','1','4','&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:21px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;DOD &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Laser therapy is suitable for any age group, any skin tone, and any body size. From athletes to pregnant women, from injured children to infirm&amp;nbsp;elderly people, from acute injuries to chronic conditions: the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;DOD &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Laser protocols can be tailored to the specific individual.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:21px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;There are no foreseeable risks associated with laser therapy when administrated by&amp;nbsp;trained clinicians. Laser therapy is a safe and effective therapy, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;DOD L&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;aser devices&amp;nbsp;have been tested for safety and effectiveness and approved by the CE and FDA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:21px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 15px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:21px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Laser therapy uses selected wavelengths of light to stimulate key molecules in human tissues. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:21px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Decades of medical research have identified the wavelengths, energy level and frequencies that induce changes in cellular metabolism (Photobiostimulation), for instance melanin absorbing sunlight energy changes the skin&amp;#39;s pigmentation. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:21px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;DOD Laser delivers energy from superficial to deep tissues activating a cascade of photochemical reactions that promotes cell function, enabling treated tissues to accelerate the stages of the healing process and reduce pain sensation. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:21px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This is a safe and non-invasive technique that uses the body&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;’&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;s own reparative processes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('150','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;980nm 1470nm diode laser can be used for:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;1) Repetitive Strain Injuries&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;2) Chronic Back Pain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;3) Sport injuries&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;4) Musculoskeletal conditions in pregnancy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;5) Post Surgical Rehabilitation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;6) Chronic Neck Pain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;7) Chronic wrist pain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;8) Scar Hypersensitivity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;9) Analgesic Effect for People Allergic to Drugs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;10) Fibromyalgia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;11) Diabetic Wounds&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;12) Chronic Non-Healing Wounds&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;13) Post Surgical Wound Healing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;14) Hallux valgus-bursitis&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;15) Toenail Fungus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;16) Plantar Fasciitis&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;17) Tarsal tunnel syndrome&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;#39;Segoe UI&amp;#39;;color: rgb(5, 5, 5);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;18) Arthritis-Osteoarthritis&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202009/1601459023d746c8.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('151','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Laser lipolysis is also called fiber&amp;nbsp;lipolysis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;It uses a fat locator to locate the fat layer, uses an extremely fine optical fiber catheter to extend into the fat layer, uses the high energy emitted by the laser to break down fat cells, and then uses the optical fiber head to drain the melted fat to achieve the visual effect of slimming and shaping.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202010/160206196277b37f.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Three-month effect of laser lipolysis and face-lifting:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202010/1602062005ee236e.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Features of laser lipolysis:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Anesthesia: local anesthesia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Trauma: No operation, with a needle stick mouth of 0.1cm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Advantages: Laser can stimulate the reorganization of subcutaneous collagen tissue, increase the ability of skin to shrink and restore elasticity after surgery, and promote skin to become smooth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Adapt to the crowd: shaping fine parts of the body, not suitable for people with serious fat accumulation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('152','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Whether outpatient minimally invasive laser therapies under local anesthesia or complicated clinical procedures in the operating room &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;–&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;DOD Laser family with its innovative, combinable two-wavelength system enables a comprehensive range of indications for laser treatments in the ENT and larynx areas that is unparalleled.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The advantages of the tissue interactions of 980 nm (hemoglobin) and 1470 nm (water absorption) in terms of absorption, coagulation, vaporization and / or cutting are optimally exploited.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Thus, all individual treatment requirements for different diagnoses can be met exactly, even sensitive procedures in children. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Main fields of application:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Endonasal surgery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Oropharynx&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Otology&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Larynx&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Dacryocystorhinostomy (DCR)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Opt for innovative laser medicine with nearly complication-free micro-surgical precision.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202010/160275307513a9db.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('153','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);&quot;&gt;For many people who use light for skin treatment, it is important to let the photon penetrate into the skin. Since photons are absorbed and scattered by the skin tissue, the color and diameter of the incident light will affect the penetration depth of the photons.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);&quot;&gt;In this study, at six wavelengths (532nm, 632nm, 675nm, 810nm, 911nm, and 1064nm), the wavelength dependence of light transmission through human skin tissue (between the earlobe and finger) was measured in vivo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);&quot;&gt;The study found:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);&quot;&gt;1) Under a given incident beam diameter, the penetration depth of photons with a wavelength of 1064nm is deeper than other wavelengths;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);&quot;&gt;2) The transmittance at a specific wavelength gradually increases as the diameter of the incident beam increases. For some skin tissues, the transmittance of 532nm photons flattens out at about 8mm, while for all other wavelengths, the transmittance tends to saturate at about 12mm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202010/160344608585797b.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('154','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Up to 40% of women and 20% of men suffer from symptoms such as tired, heavy legs and swelling as well as prominent veins that are clearly visible under the skin. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Experts estimate that these symptoms are experienced by a significant number of individuals worldwide.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;This makes diseases of the veins one of the most prevalent conditions today. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;The primary causes include congenital &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;connective tissue weakness, hormonal changes and long stretches of standing and sitting. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Impaired veins are more than just a cosmetic problem &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(196, 189, 151); font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;– &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(196, 189, 151); font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;in the worst cases and in advanced stages, they can lead to painful skin ulcers if not treated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202010/1604049356748dc9.png&quot; title=&quot;{xunruicms_img_title}&quot; alt=&quot;{xunruicms_img_title}&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;While the heart serves as the pump &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;for transporting blood in the arteries, the veins require additional pumping mechanisms to counteract &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;the force of gravity when the body is upright. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;The transport of blood back to the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;heart by the calf muscle is supported by the valves in our veins. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://dodlaser.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202010/1604049391768532.png&quot; title=&quot;{xunruicms_img_title}&quot; alt=&quot;{xunruicms_img_title}&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;If these valves do not close properly, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;blood flows back into the legs and pools &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;in the veins which become distended &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;due to the increased pressure. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(196, 189, 151); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The condition in which veins malfun&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(196, 189, 151); font-family: SohoGothicPro-Light; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(196, 189, 151); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;tion in this way is referred to as varicose &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;veins, varicosis or venous insufficiency. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Pronounced varicose veins lead to problems with the drainage of blood &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;and typically result in complaints and complications such as heavy legs, pain, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;swelling, inflammation and varicose &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;hemorrhage. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('156','1','4','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;1470nm diode laser for EVLT Safe and simple‒the all-around solution with a built-in safety concept The 1470 nm laser energy is preferentially absorbed in the intracellular water of the vein wall and in the water content of blood. The irreversible photo-thermal process induced by the laser energy results in a complete occlusion of the treated vein.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/yPUcUuQoQ4g&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;1470nm diode laser for EVLT Safe and simple‒the all-around solution with a built-in safety concept&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;The 1470 nm laser energy is preferentially absorbed in the intracellular water of the vein wall and in the water content of blood. The irreversible photo-thermal process induced by the laser energy results in a complete occlusion of the treated vein.&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES ('157','1','4','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;The pain is broken through with minimally invasive interventions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Since no or only local anesthesia is necessary for such therapy methods and they are also suitable for multimorbid patients who are no longer fit for surgery, we speak of gentle and low-risk treatment methods.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;As a rule, such interventions are painless, and extensive pain-inducing scars are avoided, which shortens the rehabilitation phase enormously.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Another great advantage for the patient is that he can leave the hospital on the same day or the next day at the latest.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Minimally invasive pain therapy - combined with external therapies - can pave the way back to a pain-free life.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Minimally invasive - mostly X-ray-assisted - procedures&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Here, pain relievers and anti-inflammatory drugs are injected precisely at the point where the pain occurs. The advantage is that the drugs only work locally and therefore higher concentrations can be administered.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;image converter-controlled infiltrations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;diagnostic / therapeutic nerve root blocks on the cervical, thoracic and lumbar spine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;diagnostic / therapeutic facet joint infiltrations on the cervical, thoracic and lumbar spine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;epidural infiltrations on the cervical and lumbar spine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;intra-articular sacroiliac joint infiltration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Trigger point infiltration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;sympathetic nerve blocks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;diagnostic discography for intervertebral disc damage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;epidural spinal catheters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Minimally invasive procedures using diode lasers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;The exact localization of the cause of the pain by means of imaging is a prerequisite. Then a probe is inserted under local anesthesia, heated and the pain is eliminated. This gentle procedure puts much less strain on the body than a neurosurgical procedure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Denervation in chronic back pain starting from the small vertebral joints (facet joints) or sacroiliac joints (ISG)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;Percutaneous laser disc decompression (PLDD) for conservatively uncontrollable herniated discs with pain radiating into the legs (sciatica) and for acute disc damage without radiating pain.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
